data.description: Welcome to your new home at 248 Koontz Loop, nestled in the charming Sonterra neighborhood of Jarrell, TX. This beautifully maintained residence offers a perfect blend of modern comfort and small-town charm with 3 Bedrooms (all upstairs), 2 and half baths. Step inside to discover a thoughtfully designed interior boasting an open floor plan. The heart of the home is the well-appointed kitchen featuring tastefully blue cabinets & granite countertops. The adjacent dining area is perfect for intimate meals or hosting dinner parties. Sonterra residents enjoy a beautiful community pool with a club house.  This home at 248 Koontz Loop offers a wonderful opportunity to embrace a lifestyle of comfort, convenience, and community. Schedule your showing today and discover the charm of Sonterra living!
